title: The one that got away-Katy Perry cover Jannina W
description:
With this song I want to pay tribute to a fan of mine who passed away early in November 2014.
Roman Huicoechea died after having a tragic accident.

A friend of him (Ale Balbiaux) informed me about this great loss and told me that his greatest wish was to hear me singing the song "The one that go away" of Katy Perry.

So dear Roman this song is for you. Rest in peace.

My condolences to the next in kind and his best friend Alejandra and his girlfriend Karen.

Jannina

title: Skyscraper - Demi Lovato Cover by Jannina W
description:
Here is my second home recorded song! (Please click "Show more")This one was probably one of the most frustrating since I had to do many many maaaaannnyyy takes because at the first time I accidentally deleted the video and only had the audio so I had to delete the audio and start over again and the other time I accidentally did it the other way round. I also faced many interruptions so I had to start over again and again. 

My voice then started to crack up so I did a short break. After thousands of retrys I finally decided "If it doesn't work this time, I quit" so I just did it and that's what came out. I'm not super-duper happy with the results but I'm okay with it so I will upload it anyway since it took me a lot of time and I don't want to just throw it in the trash. I really, really hope you like it (even just a bit is okay for me) and please make sure to like, comment, share and subscribe!

P.s. in the video I just came back from my schools seminar but I really wanted to cover a song so I just straight away did it. My face may look a bit tired or pale. I really wanted to.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AhUhPWICDaE&list=UUhFzJ0bYwztKa4H4oF8fOvw
